---
title: Business Insights & Small Business Tax Advice
description: High-intent financial strategies and deep-dive tax analysis tailored for high-growth small business structures.
layout: layouts/blog-base.njk
---

<style>
  .post-card {
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74, 93, 78, 0.1);
  }
  .post-card h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }
  .post-card h2 a {
    color: var(--charcoal);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .post-card h2 a:hover {
    color: var(--dark-sage);
  }
  .excerpt {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #444;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;
  }
  .read-more {
    color: var(--sage);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>

<section class="blog-intro" style="margin-bottom: 4rem; text-align: center;">
  <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: var(--dark-sage);">
    Strategic insights, tax code analysis, and operational financial planning built exclusively for modern entrepreneurs.
  </p>
</section>

<div class="posts-list">
  {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <article class="post-card">
      <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
      <div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--sage); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">{{ post.date.toDateString() }}</div>
      <p class="excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="{{ post.url }}">Read Strategy Overview →</a>
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
